Microsfot Teams - Let’s Talk

To join and access our Microsoft Team, click this link. If you have MS Teams installed on your computer, you may see the following prompt in your browswer.

From here you can:

  1. click “Open Microsoft Teams” to open the desktop version Teams
  2. click “Cancel” and click “Use web app instead” (my preference)

If that doesn’t work, you can access Office 365 suite applications like Email, Teams, OneDrive, Word, and Excel. Click the links to sign in to Office 365!

From the sign in page, type in your 8-digit student ID number followed by @student.necc.edu

You will be redirected to NECC’s portal login where you will sign in with your password.

You should now be signed into your account and will have access to your email and Office 365 applications, including Teams. From here you can access Teams by clicking on the Teams icon in the side bar (circled in red).

Click “Join or Create a Team” (circled in red)
